(43, 1, '2011-04-02 02:50:30', '2011-04-02 02:50:30', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nGrand Auditorium, Conservatoire de Luxembourg\r\n\r\nAfter : read more on a)Events and b) News\r\n\r\nEnsemble M&amp;M was founded in 2008. Ever since the double father and son duo- Jean and Gary Muller, Michel and Paul Mootz - has experienced growing success. In 2010 they engaged in the production of DVD that will be presented to the Luxembourgish public at a concert in the Conservatoire de Luxembourg on March 27, 2011. The program includes works by Gershwin, Bernstein, Rachmaninov and as a special highlight the world premiere of an arrangement of John Williams’ "Star Wars Suite" by John Williams, arranged by Jan Valta.\r\n\r\nEnsemble M&amp;M was founded in 2008. Ever since the double father and son duo- Jean and Gary Muller, Michel and Paul Mootz - has experienced growing success. In 2010 they engaged in the production of DVD that will be presented to the Luxembourgish public at a concert in the Conservatoire de Luxembourg on March 27, 2011. The program includes works by Gershwin, Bernstein, Rachmaninov and as a special highlight the world premiere of an arrangement of John Williams’ "Star Wars Suite" by John Williams, arranged by Jan Valta.\r\n\r\n<a href=''http://www.musicandmore.lu/wp/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/video.mp4''>video</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.musicandmore.lu/wp/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/article_bg1.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-58" title="article_bg" src="http://www.musicandmore.lu/wp/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/article_bg1.png" alt="" width="791" height="554" /></a>', 'Chopin CD Release Concert, JEAN MULLER Piano Recital', 'Grand Auditorium, Conservatoire de LuxembourgDVD', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chopin-cd-release-concert-jean-muller-piano-recital', '', '', '2011-04-02 13:14:19', '2011-04-02 13:14:19', '', 0, 'http://www.musicandmore.lu/wp/?p=43', 0, 'post', '', 0),
