(50, 1, '2011-04-02 03:17:42', '2011-04-02 03:17:42', 'Grand Auditorium, Conservatoire de Luxembourg\r\n\r\nAfter : read more on a)Events and b) News\r\n\r\nEnsemble M&M was founded in 2008. Ever since the double father and son duo- Jean and Gary Muller, Michel and Paul Mootz - has experienced growing success. In 2010 they engaged in the production of DVD that will be presented to the Luxembourgish public at a concert in the Conservatoire de Luxembourg on March 27, 2011. The program includes works by Gershwin, Bernstein, Rachmaninov and as a special highlight the world premiere of an arrangement of John Williams’ "Star Wars Suite" by John Williams, arranged by Jan Valta.', 'Chopin CD Release Concert, JEAN MULLER Piano Recital', 'Grand Auditorium, Conservatoire de LuxembourgDVD', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '43-revision-5', '', '', '2011-04-02 03:17:42', '2011-04-02 03:17:42', '', 43, 'http://www.musicandmore.lu/wp/?p=50', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
